WireGuard IPv6 Gateway Companion Plugin

Manages IPv6 routing through WireGuard tunnels on OPNsense. Solves the
limitation that all ProtonVPN (and similar) WireGuard tunnels share the
same IPv6 tunnel address by allowing unique ULA addresses per interface.

Features:
- Associate IPv6 addresses/gateways with existing WireGuard IPv4 gateways
- Automatically create and maintain IPv6 interface routes
- Mirror IPv6 gateway health status from the corresponding IPv4 gateway
- Re-add routes when WireGuard tunnels restart (WAN failover, config change)
- Gateway group support for IPv6 failover across multiple WG tunnels
